com.stormpath.sdk.tenant

Interface TenantCriteria

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Criteria<TenantCriteria>, Options, TenantOptions<TenantCriteria>

    public interface TenantCriteria
extends Criteria<TenantCriteria>, TenantOptions<TenantCriteria>
    A Tenant-specific Criteria class, enabling a Tenant-specific fluentquery DSL. TenantCriteria instances can be constructed by using the Tenants utility class, for example: 
     Tenants.options()
  .withApplications()
  .withDirectories()
